descriptionHtml:
The Diamond Sword from Minecraft. This is my 3rd 3D model I\'ve ever made and first ever mod released, so it\'s not perfect! If you guys find any bugs, errors, have any suggestions suggestions or anything feel free to contact me. Sword modeled in Cinema 4D and textured with Photoshop.

How to obtain;
Crafting [Category - MISC]: Firewood (x1), Diamond (x2)

OR

Go into your console, type the following commands 
help \"diamond sword\" 4 (the ID for the sword should pop up)
player.additem <id> <amount>

Enjoy!

Thanks,
~Arky
author: ArkAngel114
